{
  "stem": "131.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Filthy, and it taste what you give for horses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the smell of it anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Humor?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Humor.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] No humor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just some of us hoped to wake up one morning and we will be free from here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the only thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And just dreaming about food, about a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I always said, if I would have a piece of bread, I'd give my whole life away right now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it wasn't-- nobody wanted to buy my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[SOBBING] [PAUSES FOR 20 SECONDS] [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now ?] talking about food, it made you lots of time feel fat, full in your stomach, because we constantly cooked what I never knew before.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Everybody was cooking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I promised if I get out from here, every Sunday I will eat a raw potato.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I didn't keep my promise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Just once or twice I tried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I says, I can't do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 29 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had even tattooed there, I forgot to tell you all that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us and they gave us tattoo that we are all right for work, I guess, because they done that for people who were working.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 14 SECONDS] My sister and I went together, Hannah, and she got the tattoo, too, the same way like me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were always dreaming, or talking if we had a chance, that what happened to the rest of the family who came with us and everything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't want to believe that they were burned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took me from the hospital there, separate from my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took me to a city-- Liebstadt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Liebstadt, where I was working in a factory making parts of guns there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
